  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the effects of limited portion of almond consumption
      after a successful weight loss by a comprehensive weight loss plan (NovinDiet Plan) on weight
      maintenance in obese female adults.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
